extendedInfo.description: You can create your own fashion template with princesses, beautiful gowns, high heels, purses, and more. Place the princesses and items on the page anywhere you like. Add as many as you like. You can show off your princess with a collection of her favorite dresses and shoes. It's up to you and your imagination. Instructions:- Tap on Start to get started- Tap on menu to access the items- Tap on an item to add it to your page- To see more items, move finger above the items menu left to right (right to left)- Tap on the item and drag it to a spot on the page - You can re-size an item by using two fingers and pulling and stretching your fingers apart to resize- Each item you add is added on top of the previous item- Tap on Done to save to Gallery, SD card, or upload to Facebook- Drag an item over the trashcan to remove or tap on the trashcan to delete the entire page.Gallery- You can access your gallery from the main page by tapping on Gallery- Tap on a saved page to load- You can edit a page by tapping on the edit icon (pencil)- Delete the page from the gallery by tapping on the trash can.Mute- Mute the music by tapping on music icon on the main page- Mute the button sounds by tapping on the speaker icon on the main page.
